{"tid":2168735,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭家朗粉碎左報潛逃指控","createTime":"2020-08-22T03:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T03:31:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"82f3e2a850ddab6cd3fb53fdbc4d230e762d6755","tid":2168735,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T03:31:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/DMNYCMLWFFCILEWPEH7QGLH5DE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FDMNYCMLWFFCILEWPEH7QGLH5DE%2F&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThq7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=72305b13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FDMNYCMLWFFCILEWPEH7QGLH5DE%2F&h=cd3d79ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/DMNYCMLWFFCILEWPEH7QGLH5DE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鄭家朗粉碎左報潛逃指控<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_oskfGlaW6OVTgmYHRM-WmM7D_w=/5760x3840/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EF3WSA3XQNHJXG67PXNYAPWOLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_oskfGlaW6OVTgmYHRM-WmM7D_w%3D%2F5760x3840%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEF3WSA3XQNHJXG67PXNYAPWOLU.jpg&h=22518f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭家朗昨現身記者會。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】建制報章散播流言，擾亂視聽是一貫手法。建制喉舌《文匯報》及《大公報》上月以大篇幅報道，指控前香港眾志副主席鄭家朗已潛逃英國或台灣，兩報說法不一。事隔逾一個月，鄭家朗昨首度現身，承認曾因家庭及私人事務一度短暫離港，但否認潛逃。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：刪血汗工廠等醜聞 團體促還原  操控通識 教局被斥政治局<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因私事曾短暫離港<br />\n<br />\n鄭家朗昨日以新成立的教育倡議組織「教育野」發言人身份出席記者會，炮轟教育局肆意刪改通識科教科書的內容，推行洗腦教育。鄭擔任眾志副主席期間，一直主力教育議題。<br />\n<br />\n鄭親身交代動向，承認曾因家庭及私人事務短暫離港，但稱不便透露離港時。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n海關今年5月中撿獲935盒「自救口罩」，一名24歲男子被捕。眾志當時證實。。。。。。。。。。"}]}